### 1. Logowanie (użyj tylko jeśli token wygaśnie)
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@parking.pl",
  "password": "Admin@123!"
}

###

### 2. Pobranie moich danych (Me)
GET {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Odświeżenie tokenu (Refresh)
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "{{token}}",
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### 4. Wylogowanie (Revoke)
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/revoke
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"{{refreshToken}}"
